RedBlackTree<E> - Class in com.dhanish.list.structure
Self balancing red black tree structure The tree uses the Node class which holds the value and the number of children on the left and right, I use the number of children to calculate the index to emulate a list so I can keep track of the order of insertion The value is used to store the actual value Insert and delete operations take O(logN) Created by Dhanish on 12 Feb,17.
